fn\"><span class=\"fn\">as</span>.length</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAdd.hAdd\">+</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">as</span>.lengthTRAux</span> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1714-L1719","name":"List.removeAll","line":1714,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.removeAll","doc":"`O(|xs|)`. Computes the \"set difference\" of lists,\nby filtering out all elements of `xs` which are also in `ys`.\n* `removeAll [1, 1, 5, 1, 2, 4, 5] [1, 2, 2] = [5, 4, 5]`\n "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.removeAll\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">removeAll</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(xs ys : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1710-L1710","name":"List.groupBy","line":1710,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.groupBy","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `splitBy R l` splits `l` into chains of elements\nsuch that adjacent elements are related by `R`.\n\n* `splitBy (·==·) [1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 2] = [[1, 1], [2, 2, 2], [3], [2]]`\n* `splitBy (·<·) [1, 2, 5, 4, 5, 1, 4] = [[1, 2, 5], [4, 5], [1, 4]]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.groupBy\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">groupBy</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(R : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1704-L1708","name":"List.splitBy.loop","line":1704,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.splitBy.loop","doc":"The arguments of `splitBy.loop l ag g gs` represent the following:\n\n- `l : List α` are the elements which we still need to split.\n- `ag : α` is the previous element for which a comparison was performed.\n- `g : List α` is the group currently being assembled, in **reverse order**.\n- `gs : List (List α)` is all of the groups that have been completed, in **reverse order**.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.splitBy.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">splitBy</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(R : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1685-L1708","name":"List.splitBy","line":1685,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.splitBy","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `splitBy R l` splits `l` into chains of elements\nsuch that adjacent elements are related by `R`.\n\n* `splitBy (·==·) [1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 2] = [[1, 1], [2, 2, 2], [3], [2]]`\n* `splitBy (·<·) [1, 2, 5, 4, 5, 1, 4] = [[1, 2, 5], [4, 5], [1, 4]]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.splitBy\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">splitBy</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(R : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1677-L1681","name":"List.span.loop","line":1677,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.span.loop","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.span.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">span</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1666-L1681","name":"List.span","line":1666,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.span","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `span p l` splits the list `l` into two parts, where the first part\ncontains the longest initial segment for which `p` returns true\nand the second part is everything else.\n\n* `span (· > 5) [6, 8, 9, 5, 2, 9] = ([6, 8, 9], [5, 2, 9])`\n* `span (· > 10) [6, 8, 9, 5, 2, 9] = ([], [6, 8, 9, 5, 2, 9])`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.span\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">span</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(as : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1658-L1662","name":"List.eraseReps.loop","line":1658,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseReps.loop","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseReps.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseReps</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1650-L1662","name":"List.eraseReps","line":1650,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseReps","doc":"`O(|l|)`. Erase repeated adjacent elements. Keeps the first occurrence of each run.\n* `eraseReps [1, 3, 2, 2, 2, 3, 5] = [1, 3, 2, 3, 5]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseReps\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseReps</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1642-L1646","name":"List.eraseDups.loop","line":1642,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseDups.loop","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseDups.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseDups</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1635-L1646","name":"List.eraseDups","line":1635,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseDups","doc":"`O(|l|^2)`. Erase duplicated elements in the list.\nKeeps the first occurrence of duplicated elements.\n* `eraseDups [1, 3, 2, 2, 3, 5] = [1, 3, 2, 5]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.eraseDups\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">eraseDups</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#BEq\">BEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(as : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/128a1e6b0a82718382f9c39c79be44ff3284547c/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L1623-L1631","name":"List.intercalate","line":1623,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.intercalate","doc":"`O(|xs|)`. `intercalate sep xs` alternates `sep` and the elements of `xs`:\n* `intercalate sep [] = []`\n* `intercalate sep [a] = a`\n* `intercalate sep [a, b] = a ++ sep ++ b`\n* `intercalate sep [a, b, c] = a ++ sep ++ b ++ sep ++ c`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.intercalate\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">intercalate</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span